{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.dischargeAssumption\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">dischargeAssumption</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.Discharger\">Discharger</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A discharger for testing that proves side conditions using hypotheses from the\nlocal context. Always context-dependent: available hypotheses change when entering binders.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.dischargeAssumption","kind":"def","line":125,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.dischargeAssumption","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.lean#L125-L134"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.dischargeNone\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">dischargeNone</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.Discharger\">Discharger</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A discharger that fails to prove any side condition.\n\nThis is used when conditional rewrite rules should not be applied. It immediately\nreturns `.failed` for all propositions, effectively disabling conditional rewriting.\n\n**Use cases**:\n- Testing: Isolating unconditional rewriting behavior\n- Performance: Avoiding expensive discharge attempts when conditions are unlikely to hold\n- Controlled rewriting: Explicitly disabling conditional rules in specific contexts\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.dischargeNone","kind":"def","line":111,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.dischargeNone","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.lean#L111-L123"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.dischargeSimpSelf\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">dischargeSimpSelf</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.Discharger\">Discharger</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The default discharger uses the simplifier itself to discharge side conditions.\n\nThis creates a natural recursive behavior: when applying conditional rules,\nthe simplifier is invoked to prove their preconditions. This is effective because:\n\n1. **Ground terms**: Conditions like `5 ≠ 0` are evaluated by simprocs\n2. **Recursive simplification**: Complex conditions are reduced to simpler ones\n3. **Lemma application**: The simplifier can apply other rewrite rules to conditions\n\nIt ensures the cached results are discarded, and increases the discharge depth to avoid\ninfinite recursion.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.dischargeSimpSelf","kind":"def","line":91,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.dischargeSimpSelf","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.lean#L91-L109"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.mkDischargerFromSimproc\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkDischargerFromSimproc</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/SimpM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.Simproc\">Simproc</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.Discharger\">Discharger</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Converts a simplification procedure into a discharger.\n\nA `Simproc` can be used as a discharger by simplifying the side condition and\nchecking if it reduces to `True`. If so, the equality proof is converted to\na proof of the original proposition.\n\n**Algorithm**:\n1. Apply the simproc to the side condition `e`\n2. If `e` simplifies to `True` (via proof `h : e = True`), return `ofEqTrue h : e`\n3. Otherwise, return `.failed` (cannot discharge)\n\n**Parameters**:\n- `p`: A simplification procedure to use for discharging conditions\n\n**Example**: If `p` simplifies `5 < 10` to `True` via proof `h : (5 < 10) = True`,\nthen `mkDischargerFromSimproc p` returns `ofEqTrue h : 5 < 10`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.mkDischargerFromSimproc","kind":"def","line":70,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.mkDischargerFromSimproc","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.lean#L70-L89"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.Discharger\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">Discharger</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A discharger attempts to prove propositions that arise as side conditions during rewriting.\n\nGiven a proposition `e : Prop`, returns:\n- `.solved proof` if `e` can be proven\n- `.failed` otherwise\n\nBoth carry a `contextDependent` flag indicating whether context-dependent\ninformation was used during the attempt.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.Discharger","kind":"def","line":49,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.Discharger","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.lean#L49-L59"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.DischargeResult.solved\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">DischargeResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">solved</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">proof</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">contextDependent</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.false\">false</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.DischargeResult\">DischargeResult</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Discharge succeeded with the given proof. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.DischargeResult.solved","kind":"ctor","line":46,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.DischargeResult.solved","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.lean#L46-L47"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.DischargeResult.failed\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">DischargeResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">failed</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">contextDependent</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.false\">false</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.DischargeResult\">DischargeResult</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Discharge failed. If `contextDependent = true`, it might succeed in another local context. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.DischargeResult.failed","kind":"ctor","line":44,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.DischargeResult.failed","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.lean#L44-L45"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.DischargeResult\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">DischargeResult</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Result of a discharge attempt. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.DischargeResult","kind":"inductive","line":42,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.DischargeResult","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/Simp/Discharger.lean#L42-L47"}}],"imports":["Lean.Meta.AppBuilder","Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.SimpM"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.Discharger"}